<HEAD>Celebrity Backstage Soirees Offer Some Intimate Tidbits</HEAD>
<HEAD>With PM-Oscars, Bjt</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By JEFF WILSON</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>LOS ANGELES (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
